'''2015年提比里斯洪災'''，是指2015年6月13至14日間，發生在[[喬治亞|喬治亞]]首府[[提比里斯|提比里斯]]的[[洪災|洪災]]，造成了至少19人死亡<ref name="civ5">{{cite news|title=Tbilisi Flood Death Toll Rises to 19|url=http://civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=28356|accessdate=16 June 2015|work=Civil Georgia|date=16 June 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619112812/http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=28356|archive-date=2015-06-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。洪水也淹沒了[[提比里斯動物園|提比里斯動物園]]（Tbilisi Zoo），導致園內有半數的動物死亡或逃出<ref name=civ1>{{cite news|title=Tbilisi Flooding Causes Casualties|url=http://civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=28347|accessdate=14 June 2015|work=Civil Georgia|date=14 June 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180105180438/http://civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=28347|archive-date=2018-01-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="BBC">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-33125879 |title=Georgia flood: Tbilisi residents warned over zoo animals |accessdate=14 June 2015 |work=BBC News |archive-date=2015-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150823115906/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-33125879 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
[[File:Tbilisi_Flood_3.JPG|thumb]]
{{link-en|維爾河 (喬治亞)|Vere River|維爾河}}，是[[库拉河|库拉河]]的右[[支流|支流]]，其貫穿了提比里斯的瓦凱（Vake）和薩布塔洛（Saburtalo）街區，其特性為會週期性的[[突發洪水|突發洪水]]（{{link-en|Flash flood|Flash flood}}），即原本的小溪流突然氾濫成大河。先前比較顯著的災情分別曾發生在1960年、1963年、1972年，以及1995年，其中1972年的水災最為嚴重，當時也曾完全淹沒了提比里斯動物園<ref>{{cite news|title=13 ივნისის წყალდიდობა: ქრონიკა და შედეგები|url=http://www.fmabkhazia.com/news/13770-13-ivnisis-cqaldidoba-thbilisshi.html|accessdate=14 June 2015|agency=Radio Voice of Abkhazia|date=14 June 2015|language=ka|trans_title=13 June flood: timeline and consequences|archive-date=2015-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617102029/http://www.fmabkhazia.com/news/13770-13-ivnisis-cqaldidoba-thbilisshi.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 傷亡與損失 ==
[[File:Tbilisi_Flood_2015_2.JPG|thumb]]
當地時間13日[[午夜|午夜]]時分，突然下起了長達數小時的強降雨，致使洪災爆發，並挾帶大量土石沖刷流下，提比里斯東南方20公里的阿哈尔达巴（Akhaldaba）村被淹沒<ref>{{cite news|title=Reconstruction VIDEO: How did small Vere river become a raging force?|url=http://agenda.ge/news/37199/eng|accessdate=15 June 2015|work=Agenda.ge|date=15 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619220641/http://agenda.ge/news/37199/eng|dead-url=no}}</ref>。洪災導致動物園嚴重毀損，也沖毀了一條穿過維爾河的[[高速公路|高速公路]]，與鄰近的[[房屋|房屋]]，造成19人死亡，包括3名動物園的工作人員；當中一名工作人員是56歲的女性，兩週前她才因為被[[老虎|老虎]]攻擊而被迫[[截肢|截肢]]，數天前剛重返工作崗位<ref name=wp1>{{cite news|title=Zoo animals loose in streets after flooding hits Georgian capital|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/zoo-animals-loose-after-floods-hit-georgian-capital/2015/06/14/178721a0-1279-11e5-9518-f9e0a8959f32_story.html?hpid=z3&tid=sm_fb|accessdate=14 June 2015|work=The Washington Post|date=14 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619222250/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/zoo-animals-loose-after-floods-hit-georgian-capital/2015/06/14/178721a0-1279-11e5-9518-f9e0a8959f32_story.html?hpid=z3&tid=sm_fb|dead-url=no}}</ref>；而一位年輕的救援人員Zurab Muzashvili，在救出7人之後，自己不幸死亡。因為對市民的奉獻，他被追綬獎章<ref>{{cite news|title=Georgia bids farewell to officer who rescued seven before dying in Tbilisi flooding|url=http://agenda.ge/news/37626/eng|accessdate=20 June 2015|work=Agenda.ge|date=20 June 2015|archive-date=2015-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150720162729/http://agenda.ge/news/37626/eng|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

約有36人受到輕傷或中度傷害，其中大部分人在同一天先後治癒出院。14日時統計有24人失蹤<ref name=civ2>{{cite news|title=Photos: Aftermath of Deadly Flood in Tbilisi|url=http://civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=28348|accessdate=14 June 2015|work=Civil Georgia|date=14 June 2015|archive-date=2015-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150803022421/http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=28348|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，至16日仍有6人下落不明<ref>{{cite news|title=Tbilisi flooding: 14 missing people return home safe|url=http://agenda.ge/news/37122/eng|accessdate=15 June 2015|work=Agenda.ge|date=15 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619220153/http://agenda.ge/news/37122/eng|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="civ5"/>。超過40戶無家可歸，以及22,000人無電可用<ref name=civ1/><ref>{{cite news|title=Wild Rains Free Wild Animals in Tbilisi|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/06/14/wild-rains-frees-wild-animals-in-tbilisi.html|accessdate=14 June 2015|work=The Daily Beast|date=14 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619160558/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/06/14/wild-rains-frees-wild-animals-in-tbilisi.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。喬治亞政府初步估計，洪災造成的損失金額，介於4千萬<ref name=civ3>{{cite news|title=Georgia Declares National Mourning for Tbilisi Flood Victims|url=http://civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=28349|accessdate=14 June 2015|work=Civil Georgia|date=14 June 2015|archive-date=2015-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150803021904/http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=28349|dead-url=no}}</ref>至1億<ref>{{cite news|title=Georgian PM: flood damage exceeds 100m GEL|url=http://agenda.ge/news/37311/eng|accessdate=16 June 2015|work=Agenda.ge|date=16 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619220920/http://agenda.ge/news/37311/eng|dead-url=no}}</ref>
[[格鲁吉亚拉里|格鲁吉亚拉里]]間。

== 動物上街 ==
提比里斯動物園失去了將近一半的動物，至少有300隻「居民」，大部份都是死於洪災。少數的倖存者：[[河馬|河馬]]、[[老虎|大貓]]、[[狼|狼]]、[[熊|熊]]，與[[鬣狗|鬣狗]]，牠們在柵欄和籠子損壞後脫逃，在提比里斯街道亂竄，警方小組在其四周圍捕。之後部分動物被殺，部分動物被捕獲後抓回動物園<ref name=civ3/>。媒體直擊到一隻河馬脫逃至提比里斯的英雄廣場（Heroes' Square），是當地的交通樞紐，之後被[[麻醉槍|麻醉槍]]（{{link-en|Tranquillizer gun|Tranquillizer gun}}）制服的經過<ref name=civ1/><ref name=wp1/>。17日，一隻[[孟加拉白虎|孟加拉白虎]]在鄰近動物園的一座倉庫，攻擊了一名洪災倖存的男子，造成他受到致命傷<ref>{{cite news|title=Wild Animal, on the Loose from Zoo, Kills Man in Tbilisi Center|url=http://civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=28362|accessdate=17 June 2015|work=Civil Georgia|date=17 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617143144/http://civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=28362|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這隻動物最終被警方射殺<ref name="BBC News 17 June 2015">{{cite web | title= Georgia floods: Escaped tiger kills man | url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-33166224 | author= <!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> | date= 17 June 2015 | website= [[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]] | accessdate= 17 June 2015 | archive-date= 2015-06-21 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150621064949/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-33166224 | dead-url= no }}</ref>；而一隻[[非洲企鵝|非洲企鵝]]被發現在{{link-en|紅橋 (邊界)|Red Bridge (border)|紅橋}}附近游泳。該處位於提比里斯以南60公里，是與[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]的[[邊界|邊界]]橋<ref>{{cite news|last1=Najibullah|first1=Farangis|title=Penguin From Flooded Tbilisi Zoo Swims To Azerbaijani Border|url=http://www.rferl.org/content/penguin-from-flooded-tbilisi-zoo-reaches-azerbaijani-border/27077411.html|accessdate=17 June 2015|agency=[[Radio_Free_Europe/Radio_Liberty|Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty]]|date=17 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621231749/http://www.rferl.org/content/penguin-from-flooded-tbilisi-zoo-reaches-azerbaijani-border/27077411.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

